## 3. Database Schema Updates (`app/models/lab.py`)

### `Lab` Model
Defines the lab environment and requirements.
* `title`: string
* `docker_image`: string
* `duration_minutes`: int
* `tasks`: List of `LabTask` (description, verification_script, points)

### `LabSession` Model
Tracks the candidate's container.
* `user_id`, `lab_id`: references
* `container_id`: string (Docker ID)
* `status`: "Provisioning", "Running", "Submitted", "Terminated"
* `score`: int

