> [!WARNING]
> ## Security & Infrastructure Considerations
> Docker must be installed on the host running the backend. For local testing, we will connect to the local Docker daemon. For production, this usually requires a dedicated Docker Swarm / Kubernetes cluster or a hardened Docker socket connection. Are you comfortable with using the local Docker daemon for the implementation and testing of this sprint?

